tests: avoid cmp package ambiguity in go-cmp usage

Go now has a standard-library cmp package, so test files that
use github.com/google/go-cmp/cmp should make the third-party
package identity explicit. The change aliases existing go-cmp
imports as gocmp and updates only the matching Diff selectors.

